Documentation for the YaST2 OS Repair-API
-----------------------------------------

file:   README
author: Michael Koehrmann <curry@suse.de>


Creating the Makefile:
----------------------

Create the Makefile in the doc-directory "y2m_os_repair/doc/" by typing

 $ make -f Makefile.cvs

or alternatively

 $ aclocal; autoconf; automake -a; ./configure

from the main-directory "y2m_os_repair/".


Creating the document output:
-----------------------------

Type

 $ make API.dvi

to create the dvi-format,

 $ make API.ps

to create the ps-format,

 $ make API.pdf

to create the pdf-format.

If you didn't install the Makefile you can alternatively type:

 $ latex API.tex      # (2 times for generating the correct references)
 $ dvips API.dvi
 $ ps2pdf API.ps API.pdf


Required packages:
------------------

- "te_latex" : 
  for the dvi-format

- "te_latex" & "tetex" :
  for the ps-format

- "te_latex" & "tetex" & "gs_lib" :
  for the pdf-format

This version of the API-documentation is created with the packages:
- te_latex-1.0.7-196
- tetex-1.0.7-196
- gs_lib-5.50-194
